"v.极力谴责；判刑 【英】 v. 极力谴责 (disapprove of strongly; censure);判刑(inflict a penalty upon) 【考】 反义词：countenance (支持); approbation(认可)-c ondemnation(谴责)ex altation(提昇); extol(赞美) 【记】 con＋demn=damn(诅咒 )→大家诅咒→谴责 【同】 同根词：damnify(损 害); indemnify(赔偿, 补偿)派生词: condemnation (n. 谴责，定罪) 【例】 Most people are willing to condemn violence of any sort. v. 极力谴责(强烈的反对 = disapprove = censure); 判刑 【记】con共同, demn = damn(v 谴责, 诅咒)－共同诅咒－强烈谴责 【参】damnify(v 损害); indemnify(v 赔偿, 补偿) 【类】pliable: influenced = censorious: condemn易受影响的容易被影响 = 受批判的容易被责备bristle: anger = vacillate: irresolution发怒表示愤怒 = 忧郁不定表示不坚决『condone: mercy』『condemn: warning』『赦免: 仁慈』『谴责: 警告』 【反】countenance(v 支持); extol(v 赞美) 【记】con demn damn 骂→大家一起骂→谴责 condemn (v.)  early 14c., condempner ""to blame, censure,"" from Old French condamner ""to condemn"" (11c.), from Latin condemnare ""to sentence, doom, blame, disapprove,"" from com-, intensive prefix (see com-), + damnare ""to harm, damage"" (see damn). Replaced Old English fordeman. Related: Condemned; condemning."
